On Sun, 3 Aug 2003, Phil Cappellini wrote:

> Is it possible to open a rear hatch from the inside of the van, without
> damaging the door? It's locked with no key in sight.

Yes, remove the panel and you can operate the opening lever and pop the
hatch.  You can also read the number from the lock and get a key made from
that.

George Lyle
